init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In the movie, the characters are able to influence the events on the screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They can change the plot of their life, and even alter their own fate.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When you die, you will have the opportunity to resolve all of these issues.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You will be able to make amends with all of the people you have wronged, and you will be able to apologize to all of the people

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If you have a lot of unresolved issues in your life, it is a good idea to start resolving them now.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is important to note that the movie that plays at your life's end is not necessarily a reflection of the life you have led.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After all, the movie is a reflection of your life as seen through the eyes of the people who were in your life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: However, even if the movie is not an accurate portrayal of your life, it is still a good idea to watch it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The movie that plays at your life's end is also a good opportunity to reflect on your life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So if you are feeling a bit down about yourself and your life, it is important to remember that you are not alone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So don't beat yourself up about it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This movie is a gift that you will be given when you die.
